## 🌟 Why India-Specific?

**Global Standard**: 20-24°C considered "comfortable"  
**India**: 30-32°C is comfortable in summer  

**Global "Hot"**: 30°C+  
**India "Hot"**: 40°C+  

**India experiences 10-15°C higher temperatures** compared to Western countries, so the data reflects this reality!

